headline: Northern Trust’s ‘Achieving Greater Together’ Month Sets New Global Service Record
summary: CHICAGO, November 14, 2025--Northern Trust (Nasdaq: NTRS) employees have again demonstrated their commitment to community impact, dedicating a record-breaking 63,214 volunteer hours during the company’s global month of service, Achieving Greater Together. This annual initiative mobilized staff across 20 countries, supporting 1,500 nonprofit organizations and driving meaningful change on a global scale.
